.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-FUNDS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-funds \- show node on-chain and channel funds
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-funds
.SH DESCRIPTION
Shows the node operator's available funds via
.BR lightning-cli (1)
.BR listfunds :
on-chain confirmed UTXOs and local channel balances.
Returns JSON:
.nf
{
  "onchain_sat": <int>,
  "channel_sat": <int>,
  "total_sat":   <int>,
  "utxos": [{"txid":"...","output":<int>,"sat":<int>,"status":"..."}]
}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Success (returns zeros if daemon unavailable).
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-info (1),
.BR lightning-channel-open (1)
